</P>
<P>
   Hrkac, who scored 13 goals in the regular season, said it's hard
to be patient. ``But I've done it before,'' he said. \Nname:_ Mike
Heika 2 `doubtful' Oilers play Doubtful just doesn't mean what it
used to.
</P>
<P>
   A day after Edmonton coach Ron Low called injured wingers Bill
Guerin and Josef Beranek ``doubtful,'' both recovered in time to
