   FEE-CONTROVERSY (Los Angeles) _ Among the most controversial
aspects of Los Angeles Mayor Richard Riordan's proposed $4.2
billion budget is a $13 brush clearance fee _ widely blamed for
defeat of a public safety bond measure earlier this month. By Rick
Orlov. (Will move in the ``n'' California and ``a'' national news
files.)
</P>
