<SLUG> BC-EXTREME-MUSIC-REVIEW-625&AMP;ADD-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THE STRESSES OF YOUTH, THE STRAINS OF ITS MUSIC 
</HEADLINE>
  (The Week in Review) 
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For use by special arrangement
only. Asian and European points: Call Karl Horwitz in Paris for
