<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-WARNING-SIGNS-REVIEW-975(2TAKES)-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THE TROUBLE WITH LOOKING FOR SIGNS OF TROUBLE 
</HEADLINE>
  (The Week in Review) 
