<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-24 16:20 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1745 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FBC-CRASH-SURVIVOR-70     04-24 1032
