tells me he's only 17 but still was able to buy a sweet
semi-automatic pistol through one of the most cost-effective gun
brokers in town &UR; _ ``The Arizona Republic.'' By E.J. MONTINI. Story
will move in the ``A'' and ``K'' categories. &QL; 
