<P>
   ADVISORIES
</P>
<P>
   A1923 BC-GRAPHICS-FILES-NYT 111 20:00 U V
</P>
<P>
   Here is a listing of the New York Times News Service Macintosh
graphics file
</P>
<P>
   A1898 BC-SHOOTING-MEMORIAL-HNS 53 19:40 U V
</P>
<P>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)
</P>
<P>
   A1896 BC-SHOOTING-PIZZA-HNS 52 19:38 U V
</P>
<P>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)
</P>
<P>
   A1891 BC-NATO-SUMMIT-HNS 50 19:35 U V
</P>
<P>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)
